General.Name: Bonzun AB
General.Description: Bonzun AB (publ) operates as a healthcare company that provides Internet-based health services in Sweden. The company offers solutions for stress-related disorders. It also provides support services to the therapists who work with stress, cardiovascular disease, anxiety, relationship problems, etc. The company was formerly known as Papilly AB (publ) and changed its name to Bonzun AB (publ). Bonzun AB (publ) is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
